These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, gardening
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, november
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, lemon
City: colone, nizza
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby         | gardening  | camping       |
| Birthday           | november   | march    |
| Food   | lemon     | pomegranate   |
| City   | nizza      | colone     |
| Flower         | poppy | azalea      |
| Transport     | taxi       | bus           |

