.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
House: futuristic, gothic-revival
There 2 different types of food: avocado, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, badminton
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, turkish
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, filmmaking
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| House      | gothic-revival         | futuristic       |
| Food          | avocado        | strawberry |
| Sport           | badminton | tennis    |
| Flower   | daisy        | amaryllis  |
| Nationality   | turkish        | thai       |
| Hobby           | filmmaking            | hiking        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

