The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, indie
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, october
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the paramedic is on the left or right of the journalist##3
5. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
