The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, soul
House: townhouse, victorian
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, van
1. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
2. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes pink##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | lemonade   |
| Cigar         | bolivar | fonseca |
| Color   | chestnut      | pink     |
| Music-Genre   | soul        | r&b        |
| House           | townhouse        | victorian |
| Game         | backgammon    | scrabble |
| Transport     | van         | boat       |

